<p>传统强化学习的RLHF（Reinforcement Learning with Human Feedback）对一条轨迹中的所有状态动作对进行奖励加和，而大模型奖励模型仅针对整个响应提供一个奖励值。</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>传统RLHF损失函数</strong>：<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mtext>Reward_loss</mtext><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>E</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msup><mi>σ</mi><mo>+</mo></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo><msup><mi>σ</mi><mo>−</mo></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>∈</mo><mi>D</mi></mrow></msub><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>exp</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>∑</mo><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msubsup><mi>s</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo></msubsup><mo separator="true">,</mo><msubsup><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>exp</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>∑</mo><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msubsup><mi>s</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo></msubsup><mo separator="true">,</mo><msubsup><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>exp</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>∑</mo><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msubsup><mi>s</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo></msubsup><mo separator="true">,</mo><msubsup><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Reward\_loss} = - E_{(\sigma^+, \sigma^-, y) \in D} \left[ \log \left( \frac{\exp(\sum r(s_t^+, a_t^+))}{\exp(\sum r(s_t^+ , a_t^+)) + \exp(\sum r(s_t^-, a_t^-))} \right) \right]
